              <span>Versión 2026</span>
            </div>
            <div class="badge">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><path d="M22 4L12 14.01l-3-3"/></svg>
              <span>Claves originales</span>
